snippet.textDisplay: I totally get where Felix is coming from when he talks about people taking pics of him and reacting in annoying ways. He's just a normal guy when he's not making videos. He's just a worker-bee like the rest of us, except his job is more interesting and lucrative,  but the thing is....when you see celebrities/famous personalities it's like seeing a rare animal in the wild. Are you really not going to react in amazement that you were privileged to such a rare sighting?
